{"tid":1161514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普坐空軍一號拍競選影片批評紐約市長白思豪 被轟公器私用","createTime":"2019-05-19T08:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T10:45:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed1098546b36e4b48368f72f28a7e37aaecf803","tid":1161514,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpE4edng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpE4edng.jpg&h=79b39f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n川普坐空軍一號拍攝競選影片大酸對手，遭不少官員及專家痛批有道德瑕疵，甚至可能違法。（圖擷自推特）<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-19 11:07<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普日前在推特發布一則影片，內容痛批紐約市長白思豪（Bill de Blasio）表態要參加民主黨2020年總統大選提名，川普在拍攝這段影片時，由於拍攝影片的地點在空軍一號上，專家表示，川普的行為有道德瑕疵，甚至恐違法。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，川普16日推特上PO出一段影片，片中他坐在空軍一號的辦公桌上，後頭更掛著總統徽章，川普對著鏡頭抨擊白思豪說道：「若你喜歡高稅收、喜歡犯罪，就把票給他（白思豪）。」<br />\n<br />\n監督團體華府公民道德責任組織（CREW）在推特發文，表示川普應在競選期間將總統及候選人的身分界線畫清，這舉動恐違反了競選財務法的規定；該組織的律師坎特（Virginia Canter）則表示，川普此舉還犯下比違反競選財務法更嚴重的事，用後頭掛著的總統徽章來表達自己的政治立場。<br />\n<br />\n無黨派政府監督團體「共同目標」（Common Cause）的律師萊恩（Paul S. Ryan）也表示，總統在空軍一號上進行競選活動有違歷史常規，行為十分不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2794960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2794960&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=7b0eed52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2794960&h=21b3c315\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2794960</a>"},{"pid":"0a2c9b726216a3475003aa0dbf6888ce5ea18787","tid":1161514,"uid":75610,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"搭飛機嗰陣拍片都唔得痴撚線"},{"pid":"7320408bbb375787a4a7b0b4c21eda04cf4add9e","tid":1161514,"uid":215225,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:57:37.000Z","msg":"左報攻擊侵嘅方法：<br />\n將侵嘅大小事跡/決定報出黎，然後「引述」（用引號係因為有可能係作出黎）D所謂專家、白左網民嘅批評言論<br />\n咁又一單新聞+左癌又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7def0bbe674bd7f2427174ff4853815e20d3871","tid":1161514,"uid":87428,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"左膠民主 全部都係人身攻擊<br />\n同雞蛋裡挑骨頭"},{"pid":"cec3532f11b94c8ae406fd1c6e67a023f553fb15","tid":1161514,"uid":87780,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"obama 未落台之前幫Hillary 助選又點計呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e0ca4ba468a0061af9485e2316dd8f63e92f5c","tid":1161514,"uid":52946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"人身攻擊唔到班人開始發癲"},{"pid":"60071dcc619e858c5ef9e7eec582d4dce37764f6","tid":1161514,"uid":34760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"唔講以為用空軍一號炸鳩白思豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57b4687bf88868d435e58c218f9ea8c096c8f6a","tid":1161514,"uid":87780,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"Virginia Canter<br />\n@VirginiaRCanter<br />\nChief Ethics Counsel for @CREWcrew. Former White House ethics counsel for Obama and Clinton and former ethics advisor to IMF. Views are my own.<br />\n<br />\n明哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d14912efaef8619606391afb9335ac44580e1f3","tid":1161514,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"日日都被轟嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班白左華媒有邊日唔轟呀侵? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a